{"tid":2216022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾被魔警180度扭手腕 心理創傷至今未能得治","createTime":"2020-09-24T11:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T16:18:32.000Z","uid":321059,"like":54,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7c71bc497e95c2b00f9f8373e27a8ccf5d1b59","tid":2216022,"uid":321059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nBOMc8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nBOMc8.png&h=b68a9363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱憶述他沒有反抗，卻仍被警察無理壓頸和180度扭轉右手手腕，他指當時足足有30多個小時右手感到麻痺，一度連拿筆或用電腦也不敢，因擔心手腕會永久損傷。直至一年後的今日右手雖然看似無後遺症，「<span class=\"red\">但仍有啲心理影響，嗰個心理影響係會源自於⋯⋯執法者對你無緣無故，你完全理解唔到嘅仇恨</span>」。事發半年後，手傷雖癒，心理創傷卻久久未能得治，憂慮也難息止。因朱當天曾雖以「踢保」應對，但警方會否再次拘人檢控，卻屬未知數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200924/MVLLQCG62JFLPESFBLFDTXHLEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200924%2FMVLLQCG62JFLPESFBLFDTXHLEU%2F&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=56623d4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200924%2FMVLLQCG62JFLPESFBLFDTXHLEU%2F&h=a68a6fca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200924/MVLLQCG62JFLPESFBLFDTXHLEU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">仲好意思問我哋係咪真係咁憎你哋？</span></span>"},{"pid":"a7c1ee69b61b4b16dbef6b96dce3032dbfda55c1","tid":2216022,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"342dfa9d6421a14f72ef33f25481de0d7dc80334","tid":2216022,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c063b2f35175a6344adbeeee7bff43120941bbf5","tid":2216022,"uid":155902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"扭手腕真係<img src